Timerqemt, tḥemmel ugar n lḥebb yettilin deg txeddacin n yilɣan n tɣeddiwt. Aqamum-is ubrin yebbeẓ, iwulem i lqeḍ d usenser n ubsis yeffren deg txeddacin n yimɣan d tfeɣwa d yizumbiyen. 

